Mire

Upon casting this spell, the druid commands the
ground to rise up and grasp at the feet of all
creatures in the area -- only other druids and
their followers are protected.  Affected creatures
are unable to flee, and, while they can still
fight, their restricted range of movement slows
them down.  A particularly strong creature has a
chance to break free immediately, and stronger
creatures will struggle free before weaker ones
in any case.

Command: mire
Base Cost: 85 SP
Base Recovery: medium-long
Base Effect: drain (dexterity, high, area), entangle (area)
Base Duration: varies
Guild Level: 19
